CORPORATION, A WHOLLY OWNED SUBSIDIARY OF THE COMPANY, DEVELOPS, PUBLISHES, AND DISTRIBUTES DESKTOP-BASED DATABASE MANAGEMENT APPLICATION SOFTWARE FOR MAC OS AND WINDOWS-BASED SYSTEMS. THE

