SPECIALIZED LOAN PROGRAMS INCLUDING LOANS FOR CONSUMERS, STUDENTS, AND EDUCATORS. APPLE ALSO PROVIDES LEASING SOLUTIONS FOR ITS EDUCATION INSTITUTION CUSTOMERS AND ITS BUSINESS AND PROFESSIONAL

