INCLUDING A RISE IN COMPONENT COSTS AS THE YEAR PROGRESSED AND AGGRESSIVE PRICING BY THE COMPANY ACROSS ITS PRODUCTS LINES INSTITUTED AS A RESULT OF CONTINUED PRICING PRESSURES IN THE PERSONAL

