OPTIONS

TO PURCHASE 50.8 MILLION AND 58.0 MILLION SHARES OF COMMON STOCK WERE OUTSTANDING AT THE END OF 2003 AND 2002, RESPECTIVELY, THAT WERE NOT INCLUDED IN THE COMPUTATION OF DILUTED

