$14.9 MILLION IN CASH. GOODWILL ASSOCIATED WITH THE ACQUISITION OF SPRUCE IS NOT SUBJECT TO AMORTIZATION PURSUANT TO THE TRANSITION PROVISIONS OF SFAS NO. 142. THE CONSOLIDATED FINANCIAL

STATEMENTS INCLUDE THE OPERATING RESULTS OF SPRUCE FROM THE DATE OF ACQUISITION. TOTAL CONSIDERATION WAS ALLOCATED AS FOLLOWS (IN MILLIONS).

