HAS SERVED AS A SENIOR ADVISOR TO GOOGLE, INC. AND VICE CHAIRMAN OF METROPOLITAN WEST FINANCIAL LLC SINCE 2001. HE IS A VISITING

PROFESSOR AT THE UNIVERSITY OF CALIFORNIA LOS ANGELES, FISK UNIVERSITY AND MIDDLE TENNESSEE STATE UNIVERSITY. MR. GORE WAS INAUGURATED AS THE 45TH VICE PRESIDENT OF THE UNITED STATES IN 1993.

