SOFTWARE AND PERIPHERAL PRODUCTS. FROM SEPTEMBER 1995 TO OCTOBER 1999, HE WAS VICE CHAIRMAN OF TRACINDA CORPORATION. FROM MAY 1993 TO SEPTEMBER 1995 HE WAS SENIOR VICE

