VALUE OF SECURITIES UNDERLYING IN-THE-MONEY OPTIONS AT THE END OF FISCAL YEAR 2003 (BASED ON $20.69 PER SHARE, THE CLOSING PRICE OF COMMON STOCK ON THE

NASDAQ NATIONAL MARKET ON SEPTEMBER 27, 2003), MINUS THE EXERCISE PRICE.

